snippet.title: Vara Dark - Dark Titan Enterprises
snippet.description:
Dark Titan Enterprises is the home of the streamer Vara Dark.  We provide content on Gaming and Entertainment Culture.  We also provide live gaming and discussion streams.  
Dark Titan Enterprises and Vara Dark are consumer advocates of the entertainment industry and take a hard stance against censorship. Vara believes strongly in the protection of artists' ability to express their first amendment rights to create the art they want.  She's is a life long fan of Star Wars, video games and CCG's. 

Topics we cover in the Gaming and Entertainment Industries:
Current trending topics in both industries.
 Video games ranging from FPS, MMO's, Platformer's, Metroidvania's, and RPG's from Current to Retro. 
Comic Books, Pop Culture, Anime, Movies and Television Shows such as Star Wars, Star Trek, Marvel and DC.
